<item>
            <title>[LU-17939] check seq before calling lu_last_id_fid()</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-17939</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;lu_last_id_fid() asserts on seq, since LAST_ID is only valid for normal FID and IDIF, but not IGIF. Add check before calling this function.&lt;/p&gt;

